<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="8Jun1937"><font color="red">8 June 1937</font> <i>NLMS</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to Messrs Monro Saw): I have exchanged something like three or four letters with Mr Wren Howard about the text of ULYSSES which is now finally established. </div>
